Former Kano Commissioner for Works and Infrastructural development, Muaz Magaji, has recovered from coronavirus and also discharged. Magaji who was sacked by Kano state governor over comment on late president Buhari’s Chief of Staff, Abba Kyari, diclosedhis health status on Friday on his Facebook handle. He wrote, ”To the Glory of Allah SWT, today friday 22nd May and 29th Ramadan I have been confirmed Covid-19 Negative and discharged from Isolation center!” Recall that Magaji announced that he tested positive for coronavirus.